title: Sunfly 364 June 2016 MP3+CDG Karaoke
description:
Latest and greatest Karaoke from the UK Sunfly Label.   My thanks to the original seeder over on the KAT Site.  I will up the same thing in a week or so at the proper speed of 320 kilobits per second audio sample rate once the monthly disc arrives but still waiting sigh...

Pretty bad that I can download a pirate copy before my supplier can send me a bought and paid for one!!!

WHY KARAOKE SEEDS THINK IT IS OK IN 2016 TO SAMPLE AUDIO TRACKS AT ANY OTHER SPEED THAN LOSSLESS OR 320KBPS is totally beyond me.

The default settings of course of all the cheap nasty Karaoke disc rippers out there is the lousey 128 setting and more than likely they have no idea how to change that which is very sad indeed.
